<para id="RM000000Z1E003X" category="G" type-id="8000T" name-id="CL01Y-04" from="200601">
<name>ON-VEHICLE INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000000Z1E003X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000000Z1E003X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00008ZO00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT CLUTCH START SWITCH ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the engine does not start when the clutch pedal is released.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C135434E01" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the engine starts when the clutch pedal is fully depressed.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If necessary, replace the clutch start switch assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
